Package com.dashboard.data.providers

Class TimeSeriesDataProvider

java.lang.Object
com.dashboard.data.providers.TimeSeriesDataProvider
public class TimeSeriesDataProvider extends Object
Provides data for time series graphs. The maps are created externally in their respective controllers, then fed the data from this class.

    • provideSeries

      private void provideSeries​(javafx.scene.chart.XYChart<String,​Number> destChart, String name, ArrayList<javafx.scene.chart.XYChart.Data<String,​Number>> data, int stride, float normFactor, boolean isAscending)
      Provides time series data to the destination chart. The resulting data is divided by norm factor and is interpolated using neighbor points. Stride defines the number of neighbor points to use.
      Parameters:
      destChart - The destination chart.
      name - The name of the series.
      data - The time series data.
      stride - the number of neighbors from which to take the mean.
      normFactor - the data is divided by this factor.
      isAscending - if true, enforces the time series to be ascending.
